Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們夢想著  改變未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雜音中  傳來你的哭泣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭開我  歡笑之下的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐著  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們渴求著前往未來的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻為此在過去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑著的此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:31.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:37.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:46.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:06.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:18.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:35.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:31.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午後  品嘗著柚子茶和餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:37.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的紙牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:46.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來  占卜夢境的後續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}會打開多少扇大門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…尋找的東西  究竟在何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:06.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:18.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這才發現我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快點找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:35.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在這裡哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等沉重的氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小鬼的妹妹的學校回來後就一直那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上了巴司卡維爾的人  就那麼受打擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  原因好像是埃利奧特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那個容易發脾氣的小少爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在同一所學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  聽說救了奧茲大人的就是他和他的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問一下關於那首曲子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:24.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}變遷的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可以  能不能告訴我呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆聯彈過吧  就是那時彈的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子是我寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲名叫「蕾茜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  有什麼意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  差不多該告訴我你的名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道該怎麼稱呼你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對艾達的那個態度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因為兩家不和的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他要是知道我是貝薩流斯家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必也會發怒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  總覺得不能對這傢伙撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我稍微注意一下氣氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  我剛才可是遇到大麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也遇上了很麻煩的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間  被一大群女學生圍住…痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法抽身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太讓人羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在這學校上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我大吃一驚啊  沒想到會在這裡相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  最近還好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你這傢伙會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奧特  你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你那身裝扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都24歲的人了  還穿學生制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恬不知恥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（說得一點沒錯）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會認識這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢對他動粗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你  我也不會原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲·貝薩流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝薩流斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  奧茲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我聽說奧茲·貝薩流斯在十年前就死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  里奧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奧特   我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來煩我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才會信你們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:27.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（嘎嘰嘎嘰…）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那樣  到最後都沒說上話就告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  基爾巴特君是因為完全被弟弟疏遠了而在消沉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲小姐  在為什麼事生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和平常一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的大胃無用女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴  佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼煩惱的話  就和我談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒煩惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（轟轟轟…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（依靠動物的本能察覺到了危險）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯陪你玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  我沒這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說那傢伙最近缺少作為僕人的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前丟下我一人  去陪小丑喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還對著自己妹妹  嘿嘿地傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:45.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（嘎嘰嘎嘰…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為莫名其妙的傢伙而悶悶不樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊  那傢伙明明是我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是想著別人的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那也就是說…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太·美·了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了  艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是少女啊  這就是可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直太讓人心動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…心動？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  這種感情叫作「吃醋」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼  好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要說味道的話  據說是酸酸甜甜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜歡吃酸的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種酸甜的感覺正是浪漫不可缺少的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫是什麼  好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  據說是很甜蜜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的少女開關被按下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下  佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:51.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呵呵呵呵…）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要全力幫助艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒說要讓你們兩個傢伙幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  之前就感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲小姐完全沒叫過我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  試著叫我「夏羅大姐姐」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要叫大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種細節就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開…開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要叫你大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快  快·點·叫·嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（轟轟轟…）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（依靠動物的本能察覺到了危險  之二）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:38.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,0)}（夏羅看到的幻覺）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒  佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像有了個妹妹的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼看  都只是個在調戲年輕人的大媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:57.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（佈雷克的死前訊息是「千根針」寫到一半，詳見DVD特典）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來學學關於浪漫的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐會很溫柔地教導你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學習浪漫的聖經
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如這本小說裡的一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你哭泣時的醜態明明就只能讓身為飼主的我看到」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「見到誰都會搖尾巴的賤狗需要好好調教呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  這和我現在的情況不是一模一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  那傢伙怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…夏羅大姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  艾莉絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主人公為了得到他的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了所有可用的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將競爭對手一個個排除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的結局是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  為什麼把書合上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:10:01.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（心跳心跳…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是剛才那個鏡頭  對艾莉絲來說還有點早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻這種程度的事  我已經和奧茲做過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個披著兔子皮的狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為違法契約者是由得到靈體的血來完成契約的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接接…接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲他…接…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭啊  奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是定契約時的事  直接說清楚就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會讓我解釋的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我不是兔子  艾莉絲才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲…接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯卡叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在想是誰呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是涉嫌偷竊女生制服而被逮捕的變態大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛說出來啊  扎克西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被女士們用輕蔑的眼光看著  都快讓人上癮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:04.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呀哈哈哈）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這超級M
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還帶了果汁來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖說這次沒弄清楚艾達的心上人到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總之大家都平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想慶祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快  大家都拿起杯子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  慶祝大家平安無事  乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不管怎麼看這液體都…  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只不過是加入了酒精的果汁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們一般都稱這種東西為「酒」哦  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小事就不要在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你都已經25歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（25歲）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  話是這麼說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}（24歲）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200}（人偶  20歲以上）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200}（也許看不出來  但也是20歲以上）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0}（根本不是人而是靈體）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（沒有未成年人！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  奧茲也已經25歲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很煩哦  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看  艾莉絲起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…艾莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（替身）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣啊  艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（紐扣被扯掉的聲音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中指和食指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（各位觀眾絕對不要模仿哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  她完全喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅幫幫我吧  艾莉絲她喝醉了很不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我幫你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跪下來求我吧  你這隻豬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人  而且好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰是海藻頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全神智不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾的酒量一直都很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（基爾巴特大人  那是個花瓶）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是  總是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（為什麼對我吼）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把別人的髮型稱作海藻頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  海藻頭是很偉大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了就找茬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:58.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上帽子現在很流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎  你這笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這邊也？）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  我到底哪裡笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很笨  你連這都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底哪裡笨了  你給我好好解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:15.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（抽泣抽泣）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡笨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（基爾巴特看到的幻覺）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼看都是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哈哈哈哈…）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  封印解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喝醉了  就放鬆警惕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死海產品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許和我的僕人黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦  他不是你的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我重要的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  這傢伙是我的私有物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你啊  笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（推卸責任）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你監禁在小黑屋裡  讓你寂寞死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（又是「兔子會因寂寞而死」的迷信）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從根本上來講  這要怪你對我的僕人出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多開始覺得煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲那傢伙  又在被扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨角獸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲  基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧·茲·大·人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:52.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}（心跳心跳…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:56.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（果然是遺傳嗎…）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蕾茜」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來的話  埃利奧特也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都爛醉如泥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也差不多想睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣說  但其實佈雷克完全沒有喝醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個不討人喜歡的小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙誇獎真是榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼要特意裝醉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那樣的話  會破壞在場的氣氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要這種獎勵啊  你們這群豬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上居然存在佈雷克都會注意到的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止一點  小心我拍飛你哦  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得酒量好的人很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是什麼好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼想醉  都醉不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是為了警告自己不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一直緊繃著神經的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫順的奧茲君只會讓人覺得噁心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許真的是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許侮辱我的主人  佈雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要找我茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我有話…  想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你  拜託你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請珍惜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很傷心  很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉找茬接下來是一醉就哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這酒品太普通了  一點都不好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp1}boku{\fsp22}　{\fsp1}ore{\fsp51}　{\r}\N我…？我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（boku是基爾小時候的自稱，比較青澀；ore是他現在的自稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…到底是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆試試看「咱」怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「吾」或者「偶」「基露露」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克  不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  基爾  你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你背負著這種重擔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在開始我也會努力背負一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘量不依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲  你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我想從瞭解開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事  大家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  下次和我說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事  奈特雷家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這十年來發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是…  雖說不知道發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但變得相當可愛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你不就可以少辛苦一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要討厭埃利奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並沒有做錯什麼  這點他也很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  要怎麼說才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奧特他…  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  人很聰明  性格上卻是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緣再會  奧茲·貝薩流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  里奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  埃利奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  總有一天一定可以再相見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了在那時不會被罵  能在他面前昂首挺胸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要按照我自己的方式前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那傢伙還有很多話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是關於這首曲子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有很多想問的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧  埃利奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奧特？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點頭暈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做了那個夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整幢房子在燃燒  大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我站在那片血泊中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍  沾滿了他們的血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種夢  我已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}知識即是力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我叫艾莉絲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}這算是……什麼惡夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你調查了我的過去啊  巴爾馬公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}有時知情反而會產生恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}先讓我看看吧--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你是凱賓·雷古奈德的證明！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  純白之黑